00:24.160 --> 00:25.760
"Partay," with <i>ay? </i>Really?

00:26.320 --> 00:27.720
That's the way they say it.

00:28.280 --> 00:30.720
Quit stalling and create the event.

00:30.880 --> 00:33.000
How often is your mom out
on a Saturday night?

00:33.080 --> 00:34.520
Who are all these people?

00:34.600 --> 00:35.880
They are my friends.

00:36.200 --> 00:38.880
You still haven't told me
where you know them from.

00:39.560 --> 00:41.560
You're not the only one
making new friends.

00:41.640 --> 00:43.360
If you're too chicken to do it,

00:43.440 --> 00:44.840
