-What are you doing?

00:44.920 --> 00:45.800
Let's see.

00:46.120 --> 00:48.120
Event "partay," create...

00:48.640 --> 00:50.640
-Created. Done.
-Give me my phone!

00:50.720 --> 00:52.120
-OK.
-Idiot.

00:53.880 --> 00:55.640
We'll have strangers in our house.

00:55.720 --> 00:58.160
-You're irresponsible.
-That above all else.

00:58.600 --> 01:00.200
But I know you, Samu.

01:00.600 --> 01:02.640
You only care
about that fancy girl coming.

01:03.320 --> 01:05.320
That's why you're organizing all this.

01:07.120 --> 01:07.960
Idiot.

01:10.840 --> 01:13.880
MARINA ACCEPTED THE INVITATION

01:34.720 --> 01:35.560
Ander!

01:36.680 --> 01:37.520
Ander!

01:38.440 --> 01:39.280
Ander.

01:39.560 --> 01:41.560
Can you give me a minute
to explain myself?

01:41.640 --> 01:43.120
Or will you keep ignoring me?

01:44.440 --> 01:47.720
-I don't want you to end up--
-I know! I won't end up like your sister!

01:47.800 --> 01:51.120
She was drugged and taken advantage of.
No one's gonna do that to me!

01:51.200 --> 01:52.600
...to end up like my parents.

01:52.680 --> 01:55.280
-What do your parents have to--
-My biological parents.

01:56.520 --> 01:59.080
A week ago, I went to the agency.
I asked about them.

02:01.280 --> 02:03.480
Apparently, I was ten years too late.

02:04.280 --> 02:05.720
They both died of an overdose.

02:07.240 --> 02:10.520
That shit ruins your life, man.
I can't let anything happen to you.

02:11.120 --> 02:12.040
You're my friend.

02:13.760 --> 02:15.520
Why didn't you tell me?

02:17.160 --> 02:19.000
Because... we talk about other things.

02:19.080 --> 02:22.200
We talk about cars, girls, parties,
but not that.

02:23.080 --> 02:24.600
Maybe we should, right?

02:25.840 --> 02:26.680
Yeah.

02:27.880 --> 02:31.200
We could get kebabs and see a movie,
like the old days.

02:32.640 --> 02:35.600
I'd like that, but I'm still grounded.
Because of you.

02:36.080 --> 02:37.840
Your father listens to me.

02:40.200 --> 02:41.400
I'll talk to him.

03:08.400 --> 03:09.320
All right!

03:19.640 --> 03:22.120
You were beaten
by someone who grew up in the desert.

03:22.200 --> 03:23.920
It's as if you cared for Taliban girl.

03:24.000 --> 03:26.400
-Who's saying I care for her?
-It looks that way.

03:27.480 --> 03:29.760
I think you're gonna end up
like your sister.

03:29.880 --> 03:32.960
Falling for the first person
from the slums who crosses your path.

03:33.040 --> 03:36.000
-Fuck you, Lucrecia.
-That's what you were going to do.

03:36.280 --> 03:38.280
Fuck her, to then expose her.

03:39.160 --> 03:41.000
Because if I remember correctly,

03:41.440 --> 03:43.800
