in your own home.

03:44.480 --> 03:46.560
When are you going
to cut her down to size?

03:51.040 --> 03:54.000
-I'm gonna kill you, man.
-It wasn't me, I swear.

03:54.120 --> 03:56.120
Why would I tell him anything?

03:56.400 --> 03:58.280
He's had it in for me since day one.

03:58.800 --> 04:01.720
Besides, I wouldn't tell on you.
You are my buddy.

04:01.960 --> 04:04.240
In fact,
you're the only friend I have here!

04:08.000 --> 04:10.960
