04:25.320 --> 04:27.840
I'm not telling you anything,
but there you have it.

04:30.080 --> 04:32.720
How come your parents
are letting you go to the party?

04:33.240 --> 04:35.920
-Easy, I haven't told them.
-And your brother?

04:36.160 --> 04:40.240
