04:43.000 --> 04:44.920
-And your brother?
-He's the DJ.

04:45.280 --> 04:46.960
You better like twerking.

04:47.040 --> 04:48.160
-Love it.
-Oh, yeah?

04:48.240 --> 04:49.080
Look.

04:49.680 --> 04:51.680
OK, great, then.

04:53.720 --> 04:56.440
As your lawyer, I advise you
to stop talking to the police.

04:56.520 --> 04:59.440
-Unless you want to confess.
-I have nothing to confess.

05:00.520 --> 05:02.720
You were covered in the victim's blood.

05:03.400 --> 05:05.320
A victim you knew very well.

05:06.240 --> 05:08.200
With whom you were seen
having an argument.

05:09.360 --> 05:11.720
Look, Samuel,
maybe it's not what it looks like...

05:12.200 --> 05:14.360
