05:28.200 --> 05:30.320
Nano, someone is asking for you.

05:43.080 --> 05:44.320
Great burger.

05:44.800 --> 05:46.440
-You wrecked my house.
-No.

05:47.720 --> 05:48.560
Not us.

05:48.640 --> 05:50.720
