05:52.600 --> 05:53.800
We break bones.

05:57.080 --> 05:59.240
Do you know how expensive wheelchairs are?

06:00.480 --> 06:03.360
-If you pay now, you'd be saving money.
-I need more time.

06:04.400 --> 06:06.160
People want what they don't have.

06:09.480 --> 06:10.320
Look.

06:10.960 --> 06:14.000
I'm working on getting the money,
but I'll need the weekend.

06:15.800 --> 06:17.360
I can say I didn't find you today.

06:18.200 --> 06:19.840
That you had left for the weekend.

06:21.000 --> 06:23.840
But on Monday...
I will have run out of excuses.

06:25.960 --> 06:27.000
And so will have you.

06:31.720 --> 06:34.160
I swear, if I had the money,
I'd lend it to you.

06:34.240 --> 06:35.120
