than I owe... and we all win.

06:52.720 --> 06:55.560
If they catch you breaking
into that house, you don't win shit.

06:56.120 --> 06:58.760
-You lose it all.
-Fancy girl's going to let me in.

06:59.320 --> 07:02.160
-She's coming to the party.
-You'll try to hook up with her?

07:02.920 --> 07:04.800
