The sooner the better.

07:35.880 --> 07:38.480
Why don't we go on Monday?
Can Polo make it?

07:38.560 --> 07:40.480
You ask him. He's not talking to me.

07:41.160 --> 07:43.600
Wasn't it you who wasn't talking to him?

07:43.680 --> 07:44.520
Same thing.

07:44.840 --> 07:47.040
Same thing? Let me get this straight.

07:47.480 --> 07:50.520
He brings that caveman
into your relationship,

07:51.000 --> 07:55.160
