lots of doors for you in life.

10:37.040 --> 10:40.680
If the price is getting the stink eye
from those two, that's still a good deal.

10:41.080 --> 10:44.800
Wow, a reggaeton DJ and a philosopher!

10:46.720 --> 10:47.760
Have fun.

10:47.880 --> 10:48.720
