10:57.040 --> 10:58.920
<i>Hey, Guzmán, what's up?</i>

10:59.120 --> 11:01.440
Thank you for talking to my dad.

11:01.680 --> 11:04.000
In the end, he's lifted the punishment.

11:04.880 --> 11:06.240
I'm not coming today.

11:06.440 --> 11:09.720
I'm tired from training,
so I'll talk to you tomorrow, OK?

11:09.880 --> 11:10.720
