11:11.080 --> 11:12.240
Come on, Ander!

11:27.840 --> 11:31.560
What are you doing here?
My father is in the back room.

11:32.560 --> 11:33.640
Hello, by the way.

11:34.480 --> 11:36.680
I'm a customer, Nadia. I'm here to buy...

11:37.560 --> 11:38.400
this.

11:39.800 --> 11:42.560
Asparagus?
You've come here to buy asparagus?

11:45.040 --> 11:45.880
