I guess you're not invited.

12:01.000 --> 12:01.840
Listen, Nadia.

12:02.920 --> 12:05.240
Marina is there
without my parents' permission.

12:05.360 --> 12:07.480
You don't know her
or what she's capable of.

12:08.560 --> 12:10.520
