12:14.720 --> 12:16.320
Please, tell me where she is.

12:23.920 --> 12:24.760
Nadia!

12:25.720 --> 12:27.400
Nadia, please, tell me where it is!

12:27.480 --> 12:30.560
Calm down, or I'm not going to tell you.

12:32.800 --> 12:36.520
I close in half an hour.
There's a bar across the street.

12:37.040 --> 12:40.000
Have a cup of tea while you wait,
and if you've calmed down,

12:40.520 --> 12:41.600
maybe I'll go with you.

12:43.000 --> 12:44.320
You're coming with me?

12:45.640 --> 12:46.480
No.

12:47.040 --> 12:48.200
You're coming with me.

12:48.280 --> 12:49.640
I did get an invitation.

12:49.880 --> 12:52.120
With me, they might even let you in.

12:55.640 --> 12:56.480
Sir.

12:59.760 --> 13:00.880
Your asparagus.

13:06.840 --> 13:08.280
Put it on my tab.

13:30.720 --> 13:31.920
What are you doing here?

13:34.960 --> 13:37.000
Christian invited me.

13:37.880 --> 13:39.400
I see he didn't tell you.

13:43.720 --> 13:46.400
Never mind, don't worry.
I'll introduce you to everybody.

13:46.640 --> 13:47.480
Come.

13:50.800 --> 13:51.640
Omar.

13:52.840 --> 13:54.760
This is my friend, Omar. Ander.

13:55.640 --> 13:58.840
He's in my class, but fortunately,
he's not a leader of tomorrow.

13:58.920 --> 14:01.040
-Can I take your jacket?
-Nice to meet you.

14:02.280 --> 14:04.520
