21:23.640 --> 21:24.520
<i>To make you dream</i>

21:24.600 --> 21:27.040
<i>I'm the starless sky</i>
<i>That can light you up, ah!</i>

21:27.120 --> 21:28.000
<i>Brother, listen</i>

21:28.080 --> 21:29.880
<i>You'll draw your dreams</i>
<i>On paper buildings</i>

21:29.960 --> 21:31.040
<i>To make them understand</i>

21:31.120 --> 21:33.560
<i>There's no triumph in the future</i>
<i>Without fighting in the present</i>

21:37.800 --> 21:38.640
Are you OK?

21:40.760 --> 21:42.760
-Yes, and you?
-I'm great.

21:44.200 --> 21:45.760
Best party of my life.

21:45.840 --> 21:47.840
Why don't you introduce me
to your friends?

21:47.920 --> 21:49.520
Those are not my friends.

21:50.160 --> 21:52.600
They are not my friends--
I'm not good with people.

21:52.680 --> 21:54.120
Or at life in general.

21:54.520 --> 21:56.680
Then why throw this party?

22:01.080 --> 22:02.760
Sorry!

22:03.360 --> 22:05.120
-Are you OK?
-Sorry. I'm really sorry.

22:05.640 --> 22:08.160
-It's OK, don't worry.
-I'm really sorry.

22:09.680 --> 22:11.000
-No problem, Samuel.
-Shit.

22:19.120 --> 22:20.480
Are you having a good time?

22:21.800 --> 22:23.600
A better time than you, for sure.

22:23.760 --> 22:25.360
You've had a sour face all night.

22:26.280 --> 22:27.880
You've been watching me, huh?

22:29.440 --> 22:30.280
Look...

22:35.080 --> 22:39.320
I also like to play, but with my luck,
I'm sure I would never get a turn.

22:39.920 --> 22:42.200
I'd rather do it without the bottle.
Want to?

22:44.760 --> 22:45.600
Truth.

22:46.520 --> 22:48.640
Why have you been looking at me all night?

22:59.440 --> 23:02.160
Why do you think
I've been looking at you all night?

23:06.160 --> 23:07.000
Kiss.

23:31.880 --> 23:32.760
Dare.

23:34.080 --> 23:35.400
Let's get out of here.

23:36.880 --> 23:37.720
And go where?

23:40.000 --> 23:41.520
Is there anybody at your place?

24:37.160 --> 24:38.480
Give me another pill.

24:38.760 --> 24:39.600
Another?

24:47.560 --> 24:49.200
Not like this, like before.

24:49.400 --> 24:50.280
Are you crazy?

24:51.440 --> 24:52.560
What are you doing?

24:53.080 --> 24:53.920
Ander!

24:55.360 --> 24:56.840
-Why are you here?
-Guzmán.

24:56.920 --> 24:58.880
You lied to me
and used me to get away...

24:59.120 --> 25:02.200
but the worst part is you did it
to come to this party. Why?

25:02.280 --> 25:03.160
Look who it is!

25:03.240 --> 25:05.560
-It's the Ken doll!
-I'm talking to my friend.

25:05.720 --> 25:08.200
He's my friend, too.
Actually, I invited him.

25:08.280 --> 25:11.040
-You're crashing.
-Yeah, I was dying to come.

25:11.120 --> 25:13.720
Let's see.
I think the chlorine from the pool

25:13.800 --> 25:15.720
must have atrophied
that part of the brain

25:15.800 --> 25:17.160
that takes hints.

25:17.520 --> 25:18.760
We don't want you here.

25:18.960 --> 25:21.200
Shall I say it in English
so you understand?

25:23.080 --> 25:24.520
-Guzmán...
-What are you doing?

25:25.000 --> 25:26.400
-What are you on?
-Nothing.

25:26.480 --> 25:28.120
-You are high!
-I'm not!

25:28.200 --> 25:29.080
You can't shut up!

25:29.160 --> 25:30.440
-I didn't take anything!
-You!

25:30.520 --> 25:32.040
-What did you give him?
-Nothing.

25:32.120 --> 25:34.960
Don't go near him again,
not even with a cough drop.

25:35.040 --> 25:36.760
Or your sister, mother, father,

25:36.840 --> 25:38.800
and your whole family
will know what you do, OK?

25:38.960 --> 25:41.160
Guzmán, I'm fine.

25:41.360 --> 25:43.600
Stop lying to me, you retard. He told me!

25:44.280 --> 25:45.120
OK?

25:45.600 --> 25:48.360
If it's about joints, pills,
or cheap hair gel, I trust him.

25:49.840 --> 25:52.560
Don't yell at him. He's so dumb,
he told me unintentionally.

25:52.640 --> 25:53.640
Fuck off, Guzmán!

25:53.920 --> 25:56.000
Fuck you, too! And fuck you!

25:56.760 --> 25:58.240
You hear me? Fuck all of you!

26:01.240 --> 26:03.960
Maybe I'll wind up having a good time
after all.

26:29.640 --> 26:31.640
-Nadia, did you drink?
-Only punch.

26:33.480 --> 26:35.960
That punch is loaded with sugar.

26:36.120 --> 26:38.520
Samu! The cops!

26:39.440 --> 26:40.280
The cops!

26:51.080 --> 26:54.640
Polo, have you told your mothers
you are coming with us to Sardinia

26:55.000 --> 26:56.040
for Easter?

26:56.880 --> 26:58.440
I may have other plans.

27:00.080 --> 27:01.880
I need to think. I don't know if I'll go.

27:02.440 --> 27:04.240
Whatever Guzmán says, surely.

27:05.720 --> 27:06.560
Excuse me?

27:08.120 --> 27:09.480
Wow, you're talking to me.

27:10.320 --> 27:13.040
-Carla, this is not the mom--
-Come now, kid.

27:13.200 --> 27:15.800
After the fortune your mothers
have spent on speech therapists!

27:25.600 --> 27:27.560
Please, don't tag the wall, OK?

27:30.240 --> 27:32.440
Or what? They'll take away your hot tub?

27:33.200 --> 27:36.920
You think I'm the typical rich girl
who's had nothing bad happen to her?

27:37.320 --> 27:38.240
Actually, yes.

27:48.760 --> 27:51.960
-There's something you should know.
-Oh, really?

27:53.480 --> 27:54.320
OK, then.

27:55.200 --> 27:56.040
Truth.

27:57.880 --> 27:59.240
What should I know?

29:00.680 --> 29:01.520
Where to now?

29:05.080 --> 29:08.200
-I'm going home, and so are you.
-Why?

29:09.760 --> 29:12.200
Because you all are bad
at looking down on people.

29:13.000 --> 29:15.080
At least we do it discreetly.

29:20.560 --> 29:21.920
I want to swim in your pool.

29:25.760 --> 29:27.840
The two of us, swimming in my pool?

29:29.520 --> 29:30.360
No.

29:33.360 --> 29:37.040
Shall I tell the principal...
what I saw in the showers?

29:44.440 --> 29:46.280
So swimming in my pool, huh?

29:48.920 --> 29:49.800
Fantastic idea.

29:51.120 --> 29:52.880
-Let's go?
-Let's go.

30:03.320 --> 30:04.560
You're not going to talk?

30:05.960 --> 30:09.040
OK, it's enough if you listen.
I really don't understand.

30:09.120 --> 30:12.280
Why did you have to ruin it all
if we both liked it?

30:12.560 --> 30:13.560
I panicked, OK?

30:15.760 --> 30:17.680
What if you like him better than me?

30:18.680 --> 30:21.120
Remember what you told me after the party?

30:24.680 --> 30:26.040
"I love you more than ever."

30:26.560 --> 30:28.160
I felt the same way.

30:28.520 --> 30:31.160
I loved you more than ever
because you did what you wanted,

30:31.240 --> 30:33.200
regardless of what people think.

30:35.640 --> 30:36.480
Carla!

30:38.440 --> 30:39.520
Fuck the world.

30:40.440 --> 30:42.880
-What else do you want to do?
-You want to know?

31:39.720 --> 31:40.640
Come on in.

31:44.960 --> 31:49.200
-Shit. Please, they can't see you here.
-That wouldn't be good for me either.

31:53.360 --> 31:54.920
Wait here for a moment, OK?

31:59.320 --> 32:00.160
Hello.

32:00.840 --> 32:01.680
Hello.

32:02.640 --> 32:03.720
What are you doing?

32:04.080 --> 32:05.600
Nothing. You?

32:06.960 --> 32:11.400
-You could have answered my calls.
-And you could leave me alone, right?

32:21.120 --> 32:22.480
Omar.

32:24.240 --> 32:25.760
-Have another pill?
-Stop it.

32:27.520 --> 32:29.520
Guys. You deal?

32:30.240 --> 32:31.280
Get lost.

32:32.560 --> 32:33.800
-No.
-What are you doing? Let's go.

32:33.880 --> 32:34.840
Stop.

32:37.280 --> 32:39.760
I mean, do you sell pills or anything?

32:41.680 --> 32:44.560
-Do we look like dealers?
-Ander, come, let's go.

32:45.240 --> 32:47.120
You don't look like boy scouts.

32:47.640 --> 32:49.080
-Man.
-Is he for real?

32:49.480 --> 32:50.320
Ander!

32:54.120 --> 32:56.760
Who do you think you are, rich boy? Look.

33:05.200 --> 33:06.520
Hey, leave him alone.

33:07.000 --> 33:08.120
Easy, man. Easy.

33:09.520 --> 33:10.400
Please, stop.

33:10.560 --> 33:12.560
Leave him alone.
Can't you see he's high?

33:12.880 --> 33:13.720
Please.

33:15.040 --> 33:16.040
Stop, please.

33:16.400 --> 33:17.240
Let's go.

33:17.400 --> 33:20.920
-Get out of here!
-Take your boyfriend, you fucking Muslim!

33:27.120 --> 33:31.480
See? If you'd given me a fucking pill,
this wouldn't have happened.

33:35.560 --> 33:37.000
Go fuck yourself, man.

33:37.680 --> 33:39.280
And don't call me again.

33:39.920 --> 33:40.760
Or write.

33:41.600 --> 33:42.440
Why?

33:44.840 --> 33:48.360
Why?<i></i>Are you so high you don't remember?

33:49.120 --> 33:50.840
Your friend threatened me.

33:51.320 --> 33:54.080
-And if they find out about me...
-Which part?

33:56.360 --> 33:58.480
If that gets out, you'll ruin my life.

34:00.320 --> 34:04.440
It's best if...
we don't see each other again.

34:07.080 --> 34:08.440
Best for both of us.

34:19.040 --> 34:19.880
Nadia?

34:55.120 --> 34:56.240
Are you getting in?

35:21.120 --> 35:21.960
Are you OK?

35:23.000 --> 35:24.440
I've never felt better.

35:36.240 --> 35:37.680
You've been drugged, Nadia.

35:38.480 --> 35:39.360
You're high.

35:53.360 --> 35:54.560
Where are you going?

35:55.560 --> 35:57.680
To get a towel and call a cab.

36:22.720 --> 36:23.880
What happened?

36:26.320 --> 36:27.880
What do you mean, what happened?

36:28.480 --> 36:30.400
He hurt himself in your pool.

36:32.760 --> 36:33.600
Ander?

36:34.280 --> 36:35.760
Yes, Antonio, sorry.

36:36.120 --> 36:37.760
I'm surprised.
I didn't know it was that bad.

36:37.840 --> 36:39.040
-Good morning.
-Good morning.

36:39.920 --> 36:43.200
Yes, he'll have to wear it for two weeks.
You should be more careful.

36:44.080 --> 36:46.600
It was my fault. I wasn't looking,
and he started goofing off.

36:47.920 --> 36:48.920
It won't happen again.

36:50.400 --> 36:52.080
I'll keep an eye on him.

36:55.440 --> 36:56.520
All right, then.

37:10.800 --> 37:11.640
What?

37:14.920 --> 37:16.080
It means "I'm sorry."

37:17.400 --> 37:20.800
I should have stayed out of your life.

37:23.400 --> 37:26.120
How do you say "I'm still hungover"?

37:29.480 --> 37:32.680
You remind me of May. My sister.

37:34.200 --> 37:35.800
She used to smile all the time too.

37:37.880 --> 37:42.240
Even if she felt sad on the inside.
Mainly, when she felt sad on the inside.

37:44.480 --> 37:48.280
What did you mean the other day
when you said she was lost?

37:49.200 --> 37:50.120
She drank.

37:50.640 --> 37:51.480
She smoked.

37:52.080 --> 37:53.560
Went out with boys.

37:53.640 --> 37:55.640
She wanted to be like all Spanish girls.

37:55.720 --> 37:57.640
She ended up doing what none of them do.

37:58.800 --> 38:00.480
She left home at 18.

38:11.040 --> 38:12.520
It's been two years...

38:13.760 --> 38:15.120
without any news from her.

38:15.840 --> 38:16.680
All I know...

38:17.800 --> 38:19.920
is she left my family brokenhearted.

38:21.360 --> 38:23.720
And the last thing I want
is to do the same.

38:25.520 --> 38:28.280
-I think I'm also losing myself a little.
-Nadia.

38:31.440 --> 38:33.440
We are 16 years old.

38:34.600 --> 38:36.800
If we don't lose ourselves now, then when?

38:38.560 --> 38:41.120
We have all our lives
to find ourselves again.

38:52.560 --> 38:53.640
We have a witness

38:53.720 --> 38:56.360
who saw you run bloodstained
out of the school.

38:56.440 --> 38:57.440
A witness?

38:58.080 --> 39:00.320
Of course. Some rich kid, probably.

39:01.520 --> 39:04.560
Of course, because they never lie, right?

39:04.960 --> 39:06.560
Our witness is Samuel.

39:07.120 --> 39:07.960
Your brother.

39:10.680 --> 39:11.560
Is he lying?

39:13.200 --> 39:17.240
He knows perfectly well
I would never hurt Marina.

39:17.600 --> 39:19.720
-Why?
-Because we were together.

39:31.680 --> 39:32.520
Thank you.

39:32.800 --> 39:33.640
What for?

39:35.720 --> 39:38.640
For... not taking advantage
of the situation.

39:41.040 --> 39:41.880
And for the cab.

39:42.560 --> 39:44.960
-I'll pay you back.
-No problem. My treat.

39:47.880 --> 39:49.520
Who would have thought.

39:50.320 --> 39:51.760
You are a gentleman.

39:55.920 --> 39:57.160
You surprised me too.

39:58.880 --> 40:01.440
I did not see that business
with the pool coming.

40:02.120 --> 40:03.800
Gentlemen don't mention those things.

40:04.520 --> 40:06.520
Never. Ever. OK?

40:06.680 --> 40:07.520
OK.

40:25.600 --> 40:28.200
Can I give you some advice? As a friend.

40:29.360 --> 40:30.840
-Are we friends?
-No.

40:31.760 --> 40:35.360
But we are women.
And I don't like it when men toy with us.

40:36.720 --> 40:41.000
-I don't know what you're talking about.
-Guzmán's only interested in you

40:41.080 --> 40:43.440
because he bet
he could take your virginity.

40:43.520 --> 40:46.040
To then humiliate you and tell everybody.

40:46.640 --> 40:50.000
To get back at you for threatening him
the night of the party.

40:50.920 --> 40:51.960
He's so vindictive.

40:54.800 --> 40:55.640
That is a lie.

40:56.520 --> 40:57.360
Ask him.

40:57.480 --> 40:59.280
-Ready, girls?
-Friends?

41:00.840 --> 41:02.480
Positions, and...

41:12.600 --> 41:13.440
Nadia.

41:14.880 --> 41:16.200
I swear it was her idea.

41:16.560 --> 41:18.320
And you think that's an excuse?

41:19.160 --> 41:21.960
I'd expect it from her.
But I don't know what to think of you.

41:22.040 --> 41:25.400
I had you in my pool, ready for anything,
and I didn't touch you.

41:25.480 --> 41:29.400
Not for lack of wanting to. It's true.
I could have taken advantage, but...

41:30.040 --> 41:31.920
I could've taken advantage,
but I didn't.

41:32.600 --> 41:35.160
So... I should thank you.

41:36.280 --> 41:38.480
For not going through
with your plan to humiliate me.

41:39.960 --> 41:43.440
Do you realize how disgusting it is
to even consider that?

41:44.280 --> 41:46.400
The kind of person that makes you?

41:48.400 --> 41:49.680
You're no saint either.

41:51.720 --> 41:52.560
Excuse me?

41:52.840 --> 41:55.560
You spread your legs for me in my pool,
Nadia.

42:05.240 --> 42:06.560
I had been drugged.

42:07.240 --> 42:08.080
Marina.

42:18.280 --> 42:21.280
I'd offer to pay your dry cleaning,
but I'd be lying. I'm broke.

42:21.720 --> 42:23.520
-It doesn't matter.
-Yes, it does.

42:23.760 --> 42:26.840
You're avoiding me, and I understand.
I screwed up the other day.

42:27.800 --> 42:29.360
-You didn't.
-I did.

42:29.720 --> 42:32.800
I had too much wine, vodka...
too much alcohol.

42:32.880 --> 42:34.240
I wanted to feel brave,

42:34.320 --> 42:35.920
-but I just threw up.
-Don't--

42:36.000 --> 42:38.360
I needed some Dutch courage
to tell you I like you.

42:41.040 --> 42:43.760
Samuel, I'm not good for you.
There's things about me--

42:43.840 --> 42:44.680
What things?

42:46.960 --> 42:47.800
What things?

43:01.360 --> 43:03.000
I am HIV-positive.

43:17.440 --> 43:18.440
I don't know what to say.

43:21.800 --> 43:23.000
It doesn't matter.

43:23.720 --> 43:26.640
I'm OK with you not saying anything...
to anybody.

43:39.320 --> 43:40.920
You can stay at my place.

43:41.680 --> 43:45.720
So when they show up at mine,
they'll find my mom and Samu, right?

43:47.040 --> 43:49.320
-Life sucks, Nano.
-Fucking right.

43:53.280 --> 43:56.080
Look at her. She's saying
she wants to meet so we can talk.

43:57.040 --> 43:57.920
I'll pass.

43:58.360 --> 44:01.240
If they want to spice things up,
they should find somebody else.

44:04.080 --> 44:06.760
Do you know why they need
to spice up their relationship?

44:06.840 --> 44:08.920
Because it's bland, Christian.

44:09.040 --> 44:11.480
That's why they're looking
for a good stud. Listen...

44:11.920 --> 44:13.600
The more she can compare...

44:13.680 --> 44:16.160
the more she'll see
that what she has looks expensive,

44:16.240 --> 44:19.200
but it's just a cheap plastic trinket.

44:20.640 --> 44:23.560
-So what are you trying to say?
-Don't be stupid.

44:24.080 --> 44:27.760
That guy's letting you steal
his girlfriend right under his nose.

44:27.840 --> 44:29.240
You can't pass on that.

44:30.520 --> 44:31.360
I won't.

44:32.640 --> 44:33.600
Attaboy.

44:35.920 --> 44:37.920
You can't be doing this to me, Carla!

44:38.000 --> 44:40.280
What do you mean,
you have something else to do?

44:40.840 --> 44:42.400
Do you think I'm stupid?

44:42.640 --> 44:45.800
Why don't you just say you have a date
with that fucking influencer?

44:46.840 --> 44:47.840
You know what?

44:48.680 --> 44:52.160
I pity you for letting people
boss you around like this.

44:52.240 --> 44:55.240
And for having such low self-esteem...
dear.

44:55.320 --> 44:57.680
Stop treating me like I'm being abused,
OK?

44:57.760 --> 45:00.320
You say you're progressive
and that you do what you want with men,

45:00.400 --> 45:03.520
but the only reason you agreed
to be Guzmán's fuck buddy

45:03.600 --> 45:07.760
is that he didn't want anything serious,
and you wanted him really bad.

45:11.480 --> 45:13.000
Oh, sorry.

45:13.640 --> 45:16.080
I was just putting my ovaries
on the table.

45:22.440 --> 45:23.280
Hello.

45:24.600 --> 45:26.200
Son of a bitch!

45:26.720 --> 45:29.040
Check out this shack!

45:29.960 --> 45:31.320
It's beautiful!

45:32.040 --> 45:33.160
Is this yours?

45:33.520 --> 45:37.320
Our parents bought it for us,
and we are furnishing it little by little.

45:37.840 --> 45:39.440
We got the bed last Friday.

45:40.240 --> 45:41.520
Great.

45:54.800 --> 45:56.280
Christian, do you like fish?

45:56.560 --> 45:58.160
Is that a trick question?

45:58.680 --> 46:00.760
We're about to order dinner. Our treat.

46:02.120 --> 46:04.680
-Besides, I think we owe you that.
-OK.

46:19.400 --> 46:20.240
Listen...

46:21.000 --> 46:23.120
The neighbor who called the cops told mom.

46:23.240 --> 46:25.600
So we are in trouble. What's the matter?

46:27.200 --> 46:28.040
Marina.

46:29.480 --> 46:30.680
What's wrong with Marina?

46:32.880 --> 46:34.600
She's HIV-positive, Nano.

46:40.160 --> 46:43.920
That's not the worst part.
I stood there and didn't know what to say.

46:44.000 --> 46:45.800
Instead of telling her I don't care.

46:46.080 --> 46:47.480
Besides, it's not a problem.

46:47.560 --> 46:50.840
I've been reading up online,
and nowadays, it's no big deal.

46:50.920 --> 46:53.320
Instead, I just stood there
and stared like an idiot.

46:59.320 --> 47:01.320
We have it all planned. All of it.

47:01.440 --> 47:03.160
Even our retirement.

47:03.440 --> 47:05.840
-Sometimes, it's too much, right?
-Yeah.

47:06.080 --> 47:08.280
That's why we decided to add some...

47:09.360 --> 47:13.160
-spice to our lives.
-And that would be me, right?

47:13.240 --> 47:14.200
The spice.

47:14.440 --> 47:17.240
Which one am I?
Pepper, cayenne, hot chili?

47:17.400 --> 47:18.800
Forgive us, really.

47:19.960 --> 47:22.880
But... it wasn't so horrible, right?
At least, I hope so.

47:23.920 --> 47:25.360
Didn't you have a good time?

47:27.320 --> 47:28.160
I did.

47:28.600 --> 47:30.000
Would you like to do it again?

47:48.200 --> 47:50.080
Have you ever had a threesome?

49:02.560 --> 49:04.200
I love you more than ever.

49:04.440 --> 49:05.920
I love you more than ever.

49:29.000 --> 49:30.120
He told you, right?

49:33.560 --> 49:35.400
I'm on medication. It's undetectable.

49:36.000 --> 49:38.160
That means I can't infect you.

49:43.520 --> 49:45.280
I don't care that you didn't tell me.

49:46.560 --> 49:49.360
But you kept quiet
because you were afraid I'd bolt.

49:49.440 --> 49:51.080
It's not a problem, it's normal.

49:52.480 --> 49:55.560
But that's why you told Samu,
to scare him away.

49:58.080 --> 49:59.880
-Maybe.
-Marina, please.

50:00.880 --> 50:02.760
You don't know him. You won't be able to.

50:03.080 --> 50:06.160
He'll research it, and tomorrow,
he'll know more about it than you.

50:07.680 --> 50:08.840
Why are you here?

50:09.360 --> 50:10.320
Shit.

50:12.720 --> 50:15.680
Stop toying with my brother,
and tell him the fucking truth.

50:15.760 --> 50:16.960
That you're not into him.

50:17.520 --> 50:19.120
I'm not toying with him.

50:19.640 --> 50:21.280
-I feel something, but...
-Yeah.

50:22.120 --> 50:23.560
Like with me the other night?

50:24.360 --> 50:26.040
No way. That is easy to see.

50:30.880 --> 50:32.760
You felt something, too.

50:34.000 --> 50:34.840
Didn't you?

50:36.000 --> 50:36.840
Come on.

50:38.640 --> 50:39.480
Truth.

50:41.080 --> 50:42.480
This isn't a fucking game!

50:49.200 --> 50:50.960
<i>Did you know she was pregnant?</i>

50:52.920 --> 50:53.880
Did I know?

50:55.720 --> 50:57.600
Whose baby do you think that was?

51:00.720 --> 51:03.320
Why do you think
we were going to run away together?

51:04.520 --> 51:06.200
I went to school to pick her up...

51:07.800 --> 51:09.320
I found her like that.

51:10.360 --> 51:12.480
We wanted to get as far
as we could from here.

51:14.880 --> 51:16.840
Do you know who couldn't stand the idea?

51:18.560 --> 51:20.120
Your fucking witness.

51:21.400 --> 51:22.240
Are you...

51:22.400 --> 51:23.640
suggesting...

51:24.600 --> 51:26.320
that your brother killed her?

